{"tid":1851830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【派出專家】庫德洛：美將向中國派出專家 共同抗擊新型冠狀病毒","createTime":"2020-01-30T07:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T08:02:34.000Z","uid":295732,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e95e88b89a3854bf9b9cf7666de96bd17a2e4671","tid":1851830,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普的最高經濟顧問表示，美國將派專家前往中國，幫助該國遏制新型冠狀病毒疫情。該病毒已造成170人死亡，確診病例逾7700宗。「我們將從疾病控制與預防中心(CDC)派遣最好的專家來幫助他們，」庫德洛週三告訴記者。「我們是應中國的邀請這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\nSource: Bloomberg<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.bbwc.cn/iwlgcz.html?fbclid=IwAR2DCZHXb-uSEoJK5eGnrFXabStJFf2V2KNGh6_LqrNozcnCW5Tj64JSZB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.bbwc.cn%2Fiwlgcz.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2DCZHXb-uSEoJK5eGnrFXabStJFf2V2KNGh6_LqrNozcnCW5Tj64JSZB8&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=2988deeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.bbwc.cn/iwlgcz.html?fbclid=IwAR2DCZHXb-uSEoJK5eGnrFXabStJFf2V2KNGh6_LqrNozcnCW5Tj64JSZB8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAQJGeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAQJGeO.jpg&h=32326f91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4019078bd83513dd61f1f273ad42908ec8e8b4fa","tid":1851830,"uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"習仔：唔識中醫就躝返去"},{"pid":"057a390fec9025baeca55f8277faa27bdc22d75a","tid":1851830,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"【疫情展望】手足做好防護措施，去到 Phase II. 就仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df59eb1a05c2d32537e7e653464d0e5578afe049","tid":1851830,"uid":82935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"Sir,<br />\nthis way to Hong Kong , PLEASE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831ae502b5263dd3c16910a63596e